{"tid":228199,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先無綫播搶包山算唔算係佢哋既新聞節目同埋可唔可以受贊助？","createTime":"2017-05-03T17:07:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-03T20:20:08.000Z","uid":22948,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2a7ed7594eff728fb1cc52ea14a565f325cde3fa","tid":228199,"uid":22948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:07:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/004110_875333bb965c7511103dd9d068b0478b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F004110_875333bb965c7511103dd9d068b0478b.jpg&h=2c3dcc78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k0x5wgM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk0x5wgM.jpg&h=745658d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/008tNu3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F008tNu3.jpg&h=94ca99df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/004112_692271dd7907a8e3399231826ccef87e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F004112_692271dd7907a8e3399231826ccef87e.jpg&h=ed41d18a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/004112_891a2195adf16918c7153df57ebd88aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F004112_891a2195adf16918c7153df57ebd88aa.jpg&h=73037791&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一 兩個主持係無綫新聞既記者<br />\n第二 背景動畫寫住 <span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;TVB NEWS&quot;</span><br />\n第三 兩個主持既咪牌都唔係無綫平時其他節目用既咪牌 係新聞部咪牌<br />\n第四 黃曉瑩節目完話「我哋會係現場跟進住呢一個接力賽既賽果，同埋今屆包山王同包山后既消息」 如果無睇錯節目表，之後係無專門針對搶包山既節目，呢句嘢係咪代新聞部講？<br />\n<br />\nOfca既電視通用業務守則 &mdash; 節目標準 第九章 7(f)<br />\n<br />\n凡報道本地或國際新聞的真正新聞節目，不得接受贊助。 不得把廣告材料當作新聞播送，也不得把該等材料加入新聞報告或新聞片內。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，搶包山算唔算宗教儀式？<br />\n<br />\n維基百科<br />\n「搶包山是香港長洲一年一度的特色傳統民間活動，為長洲太平清醮兩項主要活動之一，另一項為飄色巡遊。」<br />\n<br />\nOfca既 電視通用業務守則 &mdash; 廣告標準 第九章 18，19<br />\n<br />\n不得接受贊助的節目<br />\n\r18. 新聞節目及通訊局不時指令播出的節目、公布或其他材料，均 不得接受贊助。<br />\r19. 宗教儀式或其他崇拜節目不得接受贊助。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/common/policies_regulations/cop/code_tvprog_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coms-auth.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Fcommon%2Fpolicies_regulations%2Fcop%2Fcode_tvprog_c.pdf&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=68ba511f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/common/policies_regulations/cop/code_tvprog_c.pdf</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/common/policies_regulations/cop/code_tvad_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.coms-auth.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Fcommon%2Fpolicies_regulations%2Fcop%2Fcode_tvad_c.pdf&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEZUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=cff2534e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.coms-auth.hk/filemanager/common/policies_regulations/cop/code_tvad_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n求解答無綫有無觸犯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a01af6a50a7c956bb6eecce07147235768863d3","tid":228199,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:08:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3aef480c384e08dd82b65033e0504f20d49414d","tid":228199,"uid":1845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:10:27.000Z","msg":"體育 好似得"},{"pid":"37c712f911a472c3e7f265c86e54911286817364","tid":228199,"uid":22948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:14:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be4571d7c9aaed9d6a1dc3f8f65131737b0a3738","tid":228199,"uid":22948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:20:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d6ae6e8b986a4891c1a55867d4477f0ffbb23192","tid":228199,"uid":14491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:31:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a3fb2fd626fecdac2b072cd403488362e0ff15","tid":228199,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"試試投訴"},{"pid":"6c40265828742088dc92aaf58127d35d102c3c7c","tid":228199,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:42:24.000Z","msg":"某D新聞節目係無事"},{"pid":"bf3ca27cf67c3219293b54e0f778a884d0a16c04","tid":228199,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T17:45:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>某D新聞節目係無事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n投訴左先無壞"},{"pid":"52ffa95cebdf30b4e794720fc9d524b08b61eb76","tid":228199,"uid":550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-03T20:20:08.000Z","msg":"咪戇鳩啦<br />\n呢個直播係走緊法律漏洞<br />\n嗰名總之唔係XX新聞就贊助得<br />\n所以亞視嘅經濟快訊收得贊助費<br />\n但無綫嘅財經新聞就唔得<br />\n無綫嘅天氣報告都收冠名贊助<br />\n而且三色台咪牌冇寫明係新聞部專用<br />\n記者都有權做娛樂節目<br />\n另外 搶包山冇足夠證據入到係宗教節目<br />\n咁講以前直播商場搞聖誕倒數都犯哂法<br />\n佢冇好明顯嘅宗教性質內容<br />\n想打無綫都要高明少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}